<plot>A man arrives in the emergency hall with his son who has sprained his ankle in school after being bullied. The father has always told the son to never let anyone put him down, and what would "Clint" do in such a situation. However, when the attending doctor turns out to be one of those that bullied his father back in his school days, the father becomes very submissive. And now the kid takes matters into his own hands.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?353279</url></doc>
